        {
            "id": 6010044,
            "title": "Hello Kitty不怕關稅攪亂！三麗鷗5月交易量倍增 超越豐田",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>Hello Kitty 所屬公司三麗鷗（Sanrio）5 月股票交易量，超越了日本最大企業豐田汽車，主因是該公司被納入 MSCI 指數，以及其被視為對關稅風險具有韌性。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010044%2Fl%2Fb7070d1af7f9bd6075a887fb6856aad7.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010044%2Fl%2Fb7070d1af7f9bd6075a887fb6856aad7.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010044%2Fl%2Fb7070d1af7f9bd6075a887fb6856aad7.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010044%2Fl%2Fb7070d1af7f9bd6075a887fb6856aad7.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010044%2Fl%2Fb7070d1af7f9bd6075a887fb6856aad7.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010044%2Fl%2Fb7070d1af7f9bd6075a887fb6856aad7.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010044%2Fl%2Fb7070d1af7f9bd6075a887fb6856aad7.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010044%2Fl%2Fb7070d1af7f9bd6075a887fb6856aad7.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010044%2Fl%2Fb7070d1af7f9bd6075a887fb6856aad7.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010044%2Fl%2Fb7070d1af7f9bd6075a887fb6856aad7.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010044%2Fl%2Fb7070d1af7f9bd6075a887fb6856aad7.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010044%2Fl%2Fb7070d1af7f9bd6075a887fb6856aad7.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010044%2Fl%2Fb7070d1af7f9bd6075a887fb6856aad7.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010044%2Fl%2Fb7070d1af7f9bd6075a887fb6856aad7.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010044%2Fl%2Fb7070d1af7f9bd6075a887fb6856aad7.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010044%2Fl%2Fb7070d1af7f9bd6075a887fb6856aad7.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010044%2Fl%2Fb7070d1af7f9bd6075a887fb6856aad7.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">Hello Kitty不怕關稅攪亂！三麗鷗5月交易量倍增 超越豐田。</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>三麗鷗 5 月份在東京證券交易所的交易總額達 2.1 兆<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/jpyusd\">日元</a>（約 146 億美元），較上月倍增，並超越豐田的 1.7 兆<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/jpyusd\">日元</a>。根據東交所週五 (6 日) 公布的數據，豐田的交易額較上個月的 2.2 兆<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/jpyusd\">日元</a>有所下降。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>岡三證券首席策略師松本史雄（Fumio Matsumoto）表示，在企業因美國關稅而面臨獲利不確定性的環境下，能夠抵禦經濟週期影響的股票能帶來安全感。此外，三麗鷗被納入 MSCI 指數，使全球投資人更容易買進持股。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>三麗鷗上個月被納入 MSCI 明晟日本指數，股價在 5 月上漲了 12%。傑富瑞日本（Jefferies Japan L）本週上調了其目標價，預計該公司的品牌資產與授權收入將會成長。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>與此同時，豐田汽車的表現落後其他公司，僅上漲 1.5%。豐田受到美國關稅及競爭加劇等不確定性因素的影響更大。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
